 YOU HAVE CHOICE !
 If you want a slighty more challenging assignment , use the code in the "harder " folder as your starting point .if you want a slightly less challenging assignment , use the code in the "easier" folder as your starting point.
 The difference between the two starting points is the "easier " starting point, there are a few steps that are already completed for you.
 HARDER : 
 If you want a slightly more  challenging assignmant , copy all the content of the 'harder' folder into your newly created solution container folder for  this assignment , e.g.,'module4-solution'.
 EASIER :
 If you want a slightly less challenging assignment copy all the content ofnthe 'easier' folder into your newly created solutions container folder for this assignment , e.g., 'module4-solution'.